<step2>
<ptxt>While observing the screen, gently jiggle the connector or wire harness between the ECU and sensors, or between ECUs.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="F047126" width="2.775699831in" height="2.775699831in"/>
</figure>
<spec>
<title>Result</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>ERROR display does not change.</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
<atten4>
<ptxt>The connector and/or wire harness will be in momentary interruption (open circuit) if the display changes. Repair or replace the connector and/or wire harness as one of them is faulty.</ptxt>
</atten4>
